    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/78a21d8bbafd1172bcdf24f2e93dc497.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=240 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏信息</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天，“咕咕披萨”店接到了一通电话……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你好？这里是太空站，请送5份夏威夷披萨！”店长毫不犹豫地准备好披萨箱，并派送鸽子送货员前往太空。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，这次送货并不普通。在带着披萨前往太空的路上，充满了坠落的危险、障碍物，以及无法预测的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『咕咕披萨：送披萨到空间站？老板，这不对啊！』是一款挑战玩家将夏威夷披萨送到太空站的横版动作游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持披萨平衡，避免摔倒！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，玩家需要保持披萨平衡，不断向上攀登。左右平衡要掌握好，不让披萨掉落。</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/d86c48622b4edf22c46712a08459304b.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/d86c48622b4edf22c46712a08459304b.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/d86c48622b4edf22c46712a08459304b.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意各种障碍物和坠落！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在送披萨的过程中，鸽子会遇到各种障碍物，被击中会导致披萨掉落。从高处坠落时也会丢掉披萨。</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/0bb0cf5cc1d6afe8a0536034eefc261f.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/0bb0cf5cc1d6afe8a0536034eefc261f.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/0bb0cf5cc1d6afe8a0536034eefc261f.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳跃！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踩在各种平台上跳跃，完成送披萨的任务。</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供辅助模式帮助您完成任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果觉得困难，可以开启辅助模式来帮助完成任务。该模式提供了与原玩法不同的操作方式，适合不熟悉这类游戏的玩家。</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>配送准备</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好送披萨了吗？能否成功完成这次危险重重的任务，将夏威夷披萨送到太空站？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在就开始你的太空挑战吧！</p>",
